  <bioghist id="aspace_f009f63cde25a9d811e2f7ff2a2e7ba7">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Henry Wright was a city planner.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_5e5dda32cd1b7f8aebd7f00f2295c900">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes project descriptions and reports on garden cities, some of which are with Clarence Stein; housing research, some on war housing and some done with Albert Mayer; the relation of city planning to architecture; article notes written jointly with Lewis Mumford; and biographical material.</p>  </scopecontent>
